Package: CircGLMBayes
Type: Package
Title: A Bayesian analysis of a circular GLM
Version: 1.0.0
Author@R: person("Kees", "Mulder", email = "keestimmulder@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <keestimmulder@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions to perform a Bayesian circular GLM, which allows regressing a
  circular outcome on linear and categorical predictors. 
